      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AMERICAN FALCON NZ (7) resumes from a spell of three-and-a-half months after closing off last campaign in good form, the last run being a solid third over 1609m at Alexandra Park. Will need a bit of luck negotiating a very wide starting position. Former Kiwi who will have plenty of admirers. WHEELSOFORTUNE (9) produced a better effort at his latest appearance when he scored by 4 metres over 2190m at Northam. Must overcome a very wide draw but rates a leading hope in a similar race. MATERNAL DREAMS (3) should be at his peak for this. Finished second over 2130m at this track at the latest appearance a week ago. Sure to give the top fancies plenty to think about. MINK (4) is in the mix if he can recapture the form from two starts back that saw him finish second over 2242m at Narrogin.",
